<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Turbulent" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Turbulent,</orth> tumultuous, uproarious: <cit><quote>the t. surge,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 5.1.221" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. V, 1, 221</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with t. and dangerous lunacy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 1, 4</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a t. and stormy night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 3.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 2, 4</bibl></cit>.
